nodes.text: Darth Norok was a Sith Lord of the reconstituted Sith Empire who participated in the Empire's invasion of Manaan during the Third Galactic War.
Darth Norok is slated to appear in the upcoming Star Wars: The Old Republic: Legacy of the Sith. The character exists within the game files with a placeholder model.
